<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<RelativeLayout xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    xmlns:tools="http://schemas.android.com/tools"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:paddingBottom="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
    android:paddingLeft="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
    android:paddingRight="@dimen/activity_horizontal_margin"
    android:paddingTop="@dimen/activity_vertical_margin"
    tools:context="com.example.simpleui.ringstudy1.DrawActivity">



    <com.example.simpleui.ringstudy1.DrawTextView
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="match_parent"
        android:id="@+id/drawTextView"
        android:layout_alignParentTop="true"
        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
        android:text="Abstract Insufficient input modality on touchscreens causes addi- tional icons, toolbars and mode switching steps required to perform different functions. Although various methods are proposed to increase touchscreen input modality, touch gestures such as swipe are not provided when using these methods (e.g., Force Touch on iPhone 6s). This still re- stricts the input modality on touchscreens. Hence, we pro- pose SegTouch to enhance touch input while providing touch gestures in this paper. SegTouch uses thumb-to- index-finger gestures, i.e., the thumb slides on the index finger, to define various touch purposes. Based on a pi- lot study, the middle and base segments on the index fin- ger are suitable input areas for SegTouch. To observe how users leverage the proprioception and natural haptic feed- back from index finger landmarks to perform SegTouch, dif- ferent layouts on the index finger segments were examined in the eyes-free manner. Including the normal touch, which means touch input without performing thumb-to-index-finger gesture, SegTouch can provide 9 input modality, so some novel applications are enabled."
        android:textIsSelectable="true"
         />

    <FrameLayout
        android:layout_width="match_parent"
        android:layout_height="wrap_content"
        android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
        android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
        android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
        android:id="@+id/finger">

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="match_parent"
            android:layout_height="100dp"
            android:id="@+id/imageView"
            android:src="@drawable/finger"
            android:layout_alignParentBottom="true"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="true"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo1"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_1"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="left|top"
            android:layout_marginLeft="70dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo2"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_2"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal|top"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="-10dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo3"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_3"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal|top"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="60dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo4"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_4"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="right|top"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginRight="20dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo5"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_5"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="left|bottom"
            android:layout_marginLeft="70dp"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo6"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_6"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal|bottom"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="-10dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo7"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_7"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="center_horizontal|bottom"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginLeft="60dp" />

        <ImageView
            android:layout_width="wrap_content"
            android:layout_height="wrap_content"
            android:id="@+id/demo8"
            android:src="@drawable/demo1_8"
            android:layout_alignTop="@+id/imageView"
            android:layout_alignParentLeft="false"
            android:layout_alignParentStart="true"
            android:layout_gravity="right|bottom"
            android:layout_marginTop="10dp"
            android:layout_marginRight="20dp" />


    </FrameLayout>
